As a Digital Advice Business Analyst, you will work under the guidance of the Digital Advice Product Owner to enhance our Digital Investment Advice offering. In this role, you will be responsible for conducting analysis and documenting requirements in the form of user stories to maintaining and evolve the offerings goal setup and onboarding experience. You will be required to stay abreast of industry best practices, analyze abandonment points and develop a strong understanding of the underlying analytics.

As a smart, passionate, detail-oriented team player who loves interacting with a diverse set of people solving tough problems and challenging the status quo, this is an amazing opportunity to forge a new digital direction for a highly respected company that is deeply committed to reinventing itself.

